(12, 'popular-post-03.jpg', 'Mới mua máy tính', '2020-07-05', 'Sĩ Nguyên', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><s>&copy; Getty&nbsp;MINNEAPOLIS, MN</s> - JUNE 16: A Minneapolis Police officers unrolls caution tape at a crime scene on June 16, 2020 in Minneapolis, Minnesota. The Minneapolis Police Department has been under increased scrutiny by residents and elected officials after the death of George Floyd in police custody on May 25. (Photo by Stephen Maturen/Getty Images)</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Two Greenville County sheriff&#39;s deputies noticed a disturbance at Lavish Lounge just before 2 a.m., and saw a large crowd running out of the building, Sheriff Hobart Lewis said at a press conference. There was &ldquo;active gunfire from inside the building,&rdquo; Lt. Jimmy Bolt said in an initial statement, and Lewis said all the shots were fired inside.</span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Both Lewis and Bolt initially said 12 people had been wounded &mdash; with at least four in critical condition, Lewis said &mdash; but Bolt told The Associated Press that two victims were likely counted twice in the confusion at the hospital.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">No one was immediately taken into custody. Bolt told the AP that the sheriff&#39;s office was looking for two suspects, but couldn&#39;t provide names or descriptions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">&ldquo;We don&#39;t really have a person of interest that we can name,&quot; Lewis said at the press conference, later adding that authorities weren&#39;t sure what led to the gunfire.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Lewis said a &ldquo;very large crowd&rdquo; was at the nightclub for &ldquo;some type of concert.&rdquo; A post on Lavish Lounge&rsquo;s Facebook page advertised a July 4 performance by trap rapper Foogiano. An Instagram direct message from the AP wasn&rsquo;t immediately returned, but a bookings representative told the AP via text message that Foogiano was fine and his team was safe.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Coronavirus cases in South Carolina&nbsp;have risen swiftly&nbsp;and the state&rsquo;s rate of positive tests is three times the recommended level. In late June, the Upstate city of Greenville &mdash; which has experienced some of the state&#39;s highest COVID-19 rates &mdash; became the&nbsp;first city to mandate face coverings&nbsp;in South Carolina, where Gov. Henry McMaster has refused to implement a statewide mask requirement.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">McMaster&nbsp;reminded South Carolinians last week&nbsp;that he hadn&#39;t lifted restrictions on large crowds, and that those operating nightclubs illegally or holding concerts against his orders don&#39;t have to be caught in the act to face criminal charges, but instead could be charged weeks later if COVID-19 cases are traced back.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Under restrictions imposed by McMaster in March to restrict the spread of the coronavirus, gatherings of 50 or more people in a single room are off-limits. It was not immediately clear how many people were in the club at the time of the shooting.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Lewis said at the press conference that he didn&#39;t know whether the club had sought an exemption to the governor&#39;s order or secured a permit for Saturday night&#39;s event, but said it was clear that the club&#39;s patrons weren&#39;t 6 feet (2 meters) apart.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">&ldquo;It&#39;s certainly not the best situation to stop the spread of this virus,&rdquo; the sheriff said.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">A phone call and an Instagram direct message from the AP to Lavish Lounge weren&rsquo;t immediately returned, but the club posted on Facebook just before 6 a.m. that events &ldquo;have been postponed until further notice.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Lewis said the victims, whose names were not immediately released, were taken to the Prisma Health hospital in Greenville, some via private vehicle. Bolt said that of the eight wounded, some had non-life-threatening injuries and others were in critical condition, but he didn&#39;t have a tally of the latter.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Prisma Health spokesperson Tammie Epps said she did not know how many victims were in critical condition.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">___</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Associated Press journalist Mallika Sen contributed to this report from Los Angeles.</span></p>\r\n', 3, 7, 1, 1),
(14, 'liftstyle.jpg', 'Sao Việt theo đuổi phong cách', '2020-07-08', 'Hoàng Nhiên', '<blockquote>\r\n<p><s><u><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">Sao Việt theo đuổi phong c&aacute;ch &#39;c&ocirc; g&aacute;i vắt sữa&#39;</span></u></s></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">Hồ Ngọc H&agrave;, Tiểu Vy, Chi Pu... chọn v&aacute;y &aacute;o phong c&aacute;ch &quot;</span>c<span style=\"font-size:20px;\">&ocirc;</span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"> g&aacute;i vắt sữa&quot; trong những th&aacute;ng gần đ&acirc;y.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Kiểu&nbsp;v&aacute;y &aacute;o&nbsp;của phụ nữ phương T&acirc;y l&agrave;m việc trong trang trại ng&agrave;y xưa đang l&agrave; mốt nổi bật. Thiết kế c&oacute; tay bồng, cổ vu&ocirc;ng, c&oacute; thể c&oacute; một ch&uacute;t b&egrave;o nh&uacute;n v&agrave; d&acirc;y thắt nơ ở ngực. Nhiều người đẹp Việt theo đuổi phong c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y bởi ch&uacute;ng dễ mặc, đem lại vẻ nữ t&iacute;nh.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Người mẫu Kh&aacute;nh Linh l&agrave; một trong số sao cập nhật sớm xu hướng n&agrave;y. C&ocirc; khoe phong c&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n trang c&aacute; nh&acirc;n với &aacute;o trắng crop top tay bồng, quần cạp cao, nhấn bằng t&uacute;i hiệu Fendi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Tủ quần &aacute;o của Hoa hậu Đỗ Mỹ Linh c&oacute; nhiều &aacute;o &quot;c&ocirc; g&aacute;i vắt sữa&quot;. C&ocirc; thường diện c&ugrave;ng quần shorts, khoe eo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Hoa hậu Tiểu Vy diện &aacute;o thắt d&acirc;y hở eo c&ugrave;ng quần jeans. Video:&nbsp;TikTok.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Hồ Ngọc H&agrave; từng chọn một chiếc đầm hoa hồng theo phong c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y khi đi sự kiện.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Kiểu v&aacute;y tương tự cũng được Yến Trang lựa chọn, kết hợp mũ c&oacute;i v&agrave; giỏ m&acirc;y theo phong c&aacute;ch n&ocirc;ng trại.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Yến Nhi phối &aacute;o tay bồng c&ugrave;ng quần jeans ống đứng m&agrave;u nổi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Phong c&aacute;ch vintage được Thanh Hằng thể hiện c&ugrave;ng đầm trắng, băng đ&ocirc; v&agrave; gi&agrave;y đế c&oacute;i.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Hoa hậu Lương Th&ugrave;y Linh diện tr&ugrave;ng v&aacute;y Thanh Hằng. Thay v&igrave; phối băng đ&ocirc;, c&ocirc; t&ocirc; điểm cho m&aacute;i t&oacute;c bằng kẹp nơ lớn.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">Minh Hằng theo đuổi xu hướng với v&aacute;y vải đũi m&agrave;u n&acirc;u. C&ocirc; c&ograve;n phối chiếc &aacute;o hoa phong c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y với quần jeans ống c&ocirc;n.</span></p>\r\n', 4, 8, 0, 0),
